{"tid":2363053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大學生賣雜貨｜90後客房清潔員轉行街市開雜貨店 日做12小時忙到跟女友分手：租金壓力令我不能停下","createTime":"2021-01-12T02:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T06:38:32.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fc63a320298fc7cc6c9ada0feeace36c8e649a17","tid":2363053,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:24:07.000Z","msg":"「打工不能發達，要為生便要自己做生意，這是自小父母跟我說的話。」吳少權（Andy）的父母經營士多和雜貨店數十載，因兩老兩年前看上一間位於天水圍天瑞街市的店舖，眼見任職救生員的兒子辛苦打工卻只有零碎的收入，便鼓勵兒子入行，「建豐隆」因而開張。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210112/QGISX5RFLBGNXD5NTMITUAFT7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210112%2FQGISX5RFLBGNXD5NTMITUAFT7U%2F&d=REZNLD6XKc%2F2J9Njm9EJudAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=614c5bb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210112%2FQGISX5RFLBGNXD5NTMITUAFT7U%2F&h=22260051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210112/QGISX5RFLBGNXD5NTMITUAFT7U/</a>"},{"pid":"af1b138e547094471da0b0ad83cf91221a025850","tid":2363053,"uid":245484,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"到而家都唔明, 親力親為到底有咩好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd07b6f18d8fad58f8c90ab681f535caf2162da5","tid":2363053,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T03:00:14.000Z","msg":"請人囉"},{"pid":"3e6c0b562d078253223dcd22a360e76657c1d7f4","tid":2363053,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"吸血蟲孽主"},{"pid":"f52980b26b7e69eb79e898a8edfb6ccff87b4f7c","tid":2363053,"uid":107927,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T03:03:11.000Z","msg":"做生意= 幫業主打工"},{"pid":"60d7a8e6fd6aba4b818c7e4d900fddf502ea8cdc","tid":2363053,"uid":86898,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T03:05:35.000Z"